data.description: Come look at this incredible floor plan and location. Every space in this home is large and comfortable!!! A 3 bedroom and 2 bath home with high ceilings, nice trim, tile floors a beautiful fireplace. Whoo Whoo come relax by the fireplace this Christmas! The home has a fantastic large sunroom that is heated and cooled for your comfort and pleasure. This home was a "former" Parade of homes and constructed with 2x6 exterior walls to allow for more insulation and sturdy construction. It has a geothermal heating and cooling system, making this home very energy efficient. The home has a sprinkler system with irrigation well pump, whole house generator and a detached workshop. Roof is 2015, equipped with hurricane shutters. Man don't miss this deal so don't delay seeing this home and making an offer.
